{"tid":2124723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉主任：民主派及本土派有不多於24小時答覆！","createTime":"2020-07-25T15:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T17:18:51.000Z","uid":7542,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8a530a8c6db30c579b873bf383ff915e6df0d5b3","tid":2124723,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">坦白講我覺得比1個鐘都比多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n多名民主派及本土派立法會選舉參選人接獲選舉主任查詢。公民黨主席梁家傑表示，選舉主任拒絕延遲回覆的要求，參選人需於明日內回應。梁家傑指，選舉主任拒絕要求，意味參選人需於不足24小時內回覆，批評做法離譜。<br />\n<br />\n相關人士收到選舉主任查詢，需要回應對《港區國安法》、外國制裁本港、否決財政預算案及港獨主張的立場或看法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539887-20200725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539887-20200725.htm&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=617d1631\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539887-20200725.htm&h=25c73bff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539887-20200725.htm</a>"},{"pid":"20a8976f18a5d112cd69e676527420867f975a9a","tid":2124723,"uid":7542,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"咪話我唔愛國，呢度借部份極權國家方法，獻計比香港政府 DQ  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=14c96977\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a>"},{"pid":"2b7b6cc56337d79a1d39442b0043adf2554f0199","tid":2124723,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a